Package: commastyler
Type: Package
Title: Leading Comma R Source Code Formatter
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jeff Newmiller<jdnewmil@dcn.davis.ca.us>
Maintainer: Jeff Newmiller<jdnewmil@dcn.davis.ca.us>
Description: Implements a code reformatting style that continues expressions
    using commas and operators at the beginning of lines.
